name: Fair_Haven_Wood_Bookcase
reviews: Well made with a great looking finish. Easy to put together although you should have two people. Enjoy!
Exactly what I was looking for. Well made and priced fairly.
description:
The Fair Haven is a practical choice for a kid's room, play area or office. Constructed of composite wood in your choice of cherry or espresso finish, this small bookcase features two fixed shelves.
